WEBVTT

00:00:11.011 --> 00:00:15.015
NOTES FROM THE LAST ROW

00:00:21.604 --> 00:00:22.439
Sis?

00:00:28.486 --> 00:00:29.612
Dad...

00:00:34.784 --> 00:00:36.327
Killed someone.

00:00:45.712 --> 00:00:47.005
I said Dad...

00:00:52.177 --> 00:00:53.887
Killed someone.

00:00:55.805 --> 00:00:58.808
<i>But that's just your imagination.</i>

00:00:59.517 --> 00:01:00.851
It's not my imagination.

00:01:00.852 --> 00:01:02.771
I'm putting the pieces together.

00:01:04.647 --> 00:01:07.816
Then did you really see the book all torn up?

00:01:07.817 --> 00:01:11.279
Yes. I happened to see it when I went into Se-yun's room.

00:01:11.905 --> 00:01:13.740
His trash can was full of torn pages.

00:01:20.121 --> 00:01:21.039
No.

00:01:22.707 --> 00:01:24.084
Start over from the beginning.

00:01:27.253 --> 00:01:29.214
It's too early to conclude it's Se-yun.

00:01:31.633 --> 00:01:33.301
Nothing is certain yet.

00:01:36.930 --> 00:01:38.014
But

00:01:39.349 --> 00:01:40.809
Se-yun's been acting

00:01:42.227 --> 00:01:43.228
A bit strange lately.

00:01:48.358 --> 00:01:50.318
Strange? In what way?

00:01:53.571 --> 00:01:56.866
<i>He rarely comes out of his room after he gets back from school.</i>

00:02:03.414 --> 00:02:04.541
Dinner's ready.

00:02:05.834 --> 00:02:06.751
I kept calling you.

00:02:12.924 --> 00:02:14.341
We should code after dinner.

00:02:14.342 --> 00:02:17.345
Fuck that! Just leave me alone, will you?

00:02:20.431 --> 00:02:24.602
I don't give a crap about coding anymore, so don't come in here again.

00:02:41.870 --> 00:02:43.580
<i>I've never seen him like that before.</i>

00:02:49.878 --> 00:02:50.711
Hey.

00:02:50.712 --> 00:02:52.255
Why are you alone?

00:02:53.256 --> 00:02:54.132
What about Yun?

00:02:55.091 --> 00:02:56.426
He says he's not hungry.

00:02:57.177 --> 00:02:58.178
Again?

00:03:00.555 --> 00:03:02.056
He said the same yesterday.

00:03:03.558 --> 00:03:06.561
And he barely ate breakfast this morning before he left for school.

00:03:07.228 --> 00:03:10.773
What's gotten into him lately? Is something up with him?

00:03:14.194 --> 00:03:15.111
I'm not sure...

00:03:15.653 --> 00:03:17.822
I think he's been feeling down

00:03:19.157 --> 00:03:20.491
Since that day.

00:03:21.284 --> 00:03:23.244
Can't blame him. I have too.

00:03:23.953 --> 00:03:24.786
Little brat.

00:03:24.787 --> 00:03:28.791
That's no excuse to lock himself in his room and refuse to eat.

00:03:29.542 --> 00:03:30.752
I'll go get him.

00:03:31.502 --> 00:03:33.379
Honey, leave him be.

00:03:33.880 --> 00:03:35.215
I'll talk to him later...

00:03:37.508 --> 00:03:38.760
Hey, Kim Se-yun!

00:03:39.844 --> 00:03:41.053
<i>But the strangest thing...</i>

00:03:41.054 --> 00:03:41.970
Kim Se-yun!

00:03:41.971 --> 00:03:43.640
<i>...is his relationship with Mr. Kim.</i>

00:03:49.062 --> 00:03:51.439
You really don't have an appetite, do you?

00:03:56.402 --> 00:04:01.157
If we had Min-hui's braised short ribs, he'd eat a whole bowl of rice in no time.

00:04:04.077 --> 00:04:07.038
Why would you bring up a dead person?

00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:09.874
Oh yeah.

00:04:10.625 --> 00:04:11.876
You're right.

00:04:12.418 --> 00:04:14.128
Her name keeps slipping out.

00:04:15.964 --> 00:04:18.006
I'm sorry. Sorry.

00:04:18.007 --> 00:04:19.968
Eat. Eat up, everyone.

00:04:27.684 --> 00:04:30.687
Maybe it's because of the funeral.

00:04:32.355 --> 00:04:35.275
I think I keep bringing her up because it's weighing on my mind.

00:04:37.819 --> 00:04:41.322
I mean, I just feel so sorry for Min-hui.

00:04:43.283 --> 00:04:45.159
She hasn't even had a funeral yet.

00:04:46.327 --> 00:04:48.663
I heard they did find her family.

00:04:49.289 --> 00:04:51.457
She has a father who remarried,

00:04:51.958 --> 00:04:53.668
But he couldn't care less.

00:04:54.168 --> 00:04:58.088
I heard her sister was the only close blood relative she had,

00:04:58.089 --> 00:04:59.424
But even she

00:05:00.508 --> 00:05:03.845
Died of an illness last year.

00:05:06.556 --> 00:05:07.515
So then

00:05:08.349 --> 00:05:10.101
What about her funeral?

00:05:11.019 --> 00:05:12.562
That's what I'm saying.

00:05:14.188 --> 00:05:18.067
If nothing comes up, I should discuss it with the president of our church group.

00:05:18.651 --> 00:05:21.695
If that happens, we'd have to raise some funds.

00:05:21.696 --> 00:05:23.906
No, don't ask the church volunteer group.

00:05:25.366 --> 00:05:26.200
No?

00:05:26.868 --> 00:05:27.702
Why not?

00:05:28.202 --> 00:05:29.412
Fundraising or whatever...

00:05:31.831 --> 00:05:35.501
Would take too long. The funeral should be held as soon as possible.

00:05:36.169 --> 00:05:38.880
People might talk.

00:05:40.423 --> 00:05:42.592
That would be disrespectful to the deceased.

00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:46.429
If money's the issue, we can take care of it.

00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:48.431
I'll pay for it.

00:05:49.015 --> 00:05:50.683
- You will? - Yeah.

00:05:51.726 --> 00:05:52.642
Of course.

00:05:52.643 --> 00:05:55.687
She <i>did</i> work in our home for a while.

00:05:55.688 --> 00:05:58.274
We should take care of her to the end.

00:05:58.775 --> 00:06:00.401
It's the least we could do.

00:06:03.029 --> 00:06:04.072
Oh, honey.

00:06:04.697 --> 00:06:05.906
You really are so--

00:06:05.907 --> 00:06:07.116
Thanks for the meal.

00:06:10.161 --> 00:06:11.287
Thanks for the meal.

00:06:17.794 --> 00:06:19.170
Repulsive bastard!

00:06:19.670 --> 00:06:20.880
That son of a bitch.

00:06:21.506 --> 00:06:22.340
Sorry?

00:06:28.805 --> 00:06:29.972
Se-yun.

00:06:31.224 --> 00:06:32.683
He seems completely fine

00:06:33.309 --> 00:06:35.519
Whenever I see him at school.

00:06:35.520 --> 00:06:39.189
And his assignments are normal. He always writes about trivial stuff.

00:06:39.190 --> 00:06:40.649
Yes, that's right.

00:06:40.650 --> 00:06:44.112
He's like that at home but acts like nothing's wrong at school.

00:06:44.612 --> 00:06:46.239
Even plays ball with his friends.

00:06:49.367 --> 00:06:50.368
Kang.

00:06:51.202 --> 00:06:52.537
Time to revisit the hotel.

00:06:53.579 --> 00:06:55.164
- The hotel? - Yeah.

00:06:55.957 --> 00:06:58.209
Always look before you leap, as they say.

00:06:59.043 --> 00:07:01.504
It's crucial to get the facts straight first.

00:07:06.050 --> 00:07:08.093
It's time for our class. We should go.

00:07:08.094 --> 00:07:09.010
- Already? - Hurry!

00:07:09.011 --> 00:07:10.596
- See you. - Yeah.

00:07:35.872 --> 00:07:37.290
Was it really you?

00:07:39.542 --> 00:07:41.127
Se-yun.

00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:45.756
I hope it really was you.

00:07:54.557 --> 00:07:56.476
Kim Su-hun, you bastard.

00:07:57.351 --> 00:07:58.728
What the hell

00:08:00.188 --> 00:08:02.315
Did your son find out about you?

00:08:18.789 --> 00:08:20.291
I was right, Mr. Heo.

00:08:20.791 --> 00:08:21.792
About Se-yun.

00:08:29.342 --> 00:08:30.343
I see.

00:08:31.886 --> 00:08:34.180
So it was him after all.

00:08:36.140 --> 00:08:38.809
I only managed to get this by begging Jae-sik for it.

00:08:41.562 --> 00:08:42.480
We got it!

00:08:43.314 --> 00:08:44.857
We got it.

00:08:46.526 --> 00:08:47.735
So now,

00:08:48.945 --> 00:08:51.906
We just need to find out what Kim Se-yun knows.

00:08:57.161 --> 00:08:58.287
Hey.

00:08:59.247 --> 00:09:00.456
Why the long face?

00:09:01.457 --> 00:09:02.291
Sorry?

00:09:03.543 --> 00:09:05.169
What do you...

00:09:06.796 --> 00:09:08.881
Why do you look like you just ate shit?

00:09:12.426 --> 00:09:13.719
Well, it's just...

00:09:14.804 --> 00:09:16.055
Just what?

00:09:17.431 --> 00:09:18.849
You got something else to say?

00:09:19.850 --> 00:09:20.893
If so, go ahead.

00:09:25.565 --> 00:09:28.776
My mind is all over the place thinking about Se-yun.

00:09:33.739 --> 00:09:35.116
Until recently,

00:09:36.117 --> 00:09:39.579
It felt pretty satisfying to find out that Mr. Kim was a bad person.

00:09:40.663 --> 00:09:41.747
Do you know why?

00:09:44.166 --> 00:09:46.043
Se-yun was kind of annoying.

00:09:47.169 --> 00:09:50.256
He seemed to have the perfect life and everything he could ever want.

00:09:53.926 --> 00:09:55.553
But seeing him these days...

00:09:59.724 --> 00:10:01.350
I guess it really does hurt

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:04.103
To watch a friend suffer.

00:10:18.284 --> 00:10:19.744
Yeah, exactly.

00:10:20.620 --> 00:10:22.330
That's why we're helping Se-yun.

00:10:24.582 --> 00:10:25.416
Sorry?

00:10:26.584 --> 00:10:27.752
Don't you get it?

00:10:28.544 --> 00:10:32.048
If we find out what Kim Se-yun knows,

00:10:33.049 --> 00:10:37.345
We might be able to help him. Ever heard of thinking outside the box?

00:10:41.599 --> 00:10:44.100
Besides, that's the thing about friendship.

00:10:44.101 --> 00:10:47.271
Covering up the truth isn't always the best solution.

00:10:47.772 --> 00:10:50.900
Sometimes, uncovering the truth

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:55.196
And making your friend face it can be the best thing for them.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.159
Are we good now?

00:11:01.035 --> 00:11:02.411
From now on,

00:11:03.204 --> 00:11:04.830
Whenever you're conflicted,

00:11:06.499 --> 00:11:09.377
Remind yourself that we're helping your friend.

00:11:10.753 --> 00:11:11.671
Okay.

00:11:14.548 --> 00:11:15.758
By the way, Mr. Heo,

00:11:16.842 --> 00:11:18.010
I have some news.

00:11:19.303 --> 00:11:20.220
News?

00:11:20.221 --> 00:11:24.517
Se-yun's sister, Jeong-hu, is coming home on Sunday.

00:11:25.434 --> 00:11:26.852
It's Mr. Kim's birthday.

00:11:28.896 --> 00:11:30.356
Kim Su-hun's birthday?

00:11:30.940 --> 00:11:35.403
Se-yun is really close to his sister. They seem to stay in touch a lot too.

00:11:37.988 --> 00:11:38.989
Is that right?

00:11:41.534 --> 00:11:43.911
Then listen to every single word

00:11:44.412 --> 00:11:45.496
Those two exchange

00:11:45.996 --> 00:11:47.540
When they're alone.

00:11:48.207 --> 00:11:50.251
Something <i>will</i> come up in their conversations.

00:11:51.127 --> 00:11:52.253
That is this week's

00:11:53.170 --> 00:11:54.672
Investigative assignment.

00:12:06.892 --> 00:12:07.727
Here.

00:12:12.022 --> 00:12:13.232
Even

00:12:13.858 --> 00:12:15.401
Your autograph is cool.

00:12:16.026 --> 00:12:16.861
Like your novel.

00:12:18.529 --> 00:12:19.697
The honor is mine.

00:12:20.197 --> 00:12:23.659
Se-yun, on the other hand, has zero interest in what I write.

00:12:26.162 --> 00:12:26.996
Here.

00:12:28.789 --> 00:12:30.040
Where's Dad?

00:12:30.583 --> 00:12:32.167
The man of the hour?

00:12:32.168 --> 00:12:33.419
Dad?

00:12:34.879 --> 00:12:38.257
Your dad went to Min-hui's funeral.

00:12:38.758 --> 00:12:42.928
He'll be back this evening after running some errands.

00:12:43.429 --> 00:12:44.764
Her funeral?

00:12:45.473 --> 00:12:46.307
Of all days...

00:12:48.058 --> 00:12:49.976
So it's happening after all.

00:12:49.977 --> 00:12:51.604
It's a relief

00:12:52.104 --> 00:12:54.440
That they can finally hold the funeral.

00:12:55.316 --> 00:12:58.735
I wanted to go with him, but your dad told me to stay home--

00:12:58.736 --> 00:13:00.196
Why would you go?

00:13:02.406 --> 00:13:05.326
What do you mean, why? I'd have reason to attend, wouldn't I?

00:13:07.161 --> 00:13:08.037
I just mean,

00:13:09.330 --> 00:13:13.000
I haven't visited in a while. If both of you weren't here, it'd be...

00:13:15.252 --> 00:13:16.170
There he is.

00:13:17.087 --> 00:13:18.339
Did you just wake up?

00:13:19.381 --> 00:13:20.424
You're here.

00:13:21.717 --> 00:13:24.970
All done sleeping now, sleepyhead?

00:13:25.971 --> 00:13:28.182
Still, you managed to get him downstairs.

00:13:28.682 --> 00:13:30.309
What? What do you mean?

00:13:31.602 --> 00:13:34.020
This one's been holed up in his room lately,

00:13:34.021 --> 00:13:35.688
Gaming all day and night.

00:13:35.689 --> 00:13:37.316
You should give him a talking-to.

00:13:38.818 --> 00:13:43.280
Yun's always listened to his sister, ever since he was a kid.

00:13:43.989 --> 00:13:45.616
He was always her shadow.

00:13:48.452 --> 00:13:50.245
Then I should give him a talking-to.

00:13:50.246 --> 00:13:53.832
Hey, you little shit. Come with me. You're dead meat.

00:13:53.833 --> 00:13:55.375
I won't go easy on you.

00:13:55.376 --> 00:13:58.003
- I told you to be good, didn't I? - Excuse me?

00:13:59.004 --> 00:14:01.548
- Hey, you punk. - I'm not a little kid anymore.

00:14:01.549 --> 00:14:02.465
Hey.

00:14:02.466 --> 00:14:05.301
All right, then. Take it easy until your dad gets home.

00:14:05.302 --> 00:14:07.303
- Don't move. - I have a lot of work to do.

00:14:07.304 --> 00:14:08.889
Let go. Three, two...

00:14:33.247 --> 00:14:34.665
How shameless.

00:14:35.332 --> 00:14:38.252
He went to that woman's funeral on a family day?

00:14:41.505 --> 00:14:45.550
He must feel a little guilty for cheating, seeing how he wouldn't let Mom go.

00:14:45.551 --> 00:14:48.511
<i>As I expected, Jeong-hu knows too.</i>

00:14:48.512 --> 00:14:50.806
But how can Mom be so blind to all of this?

00:14:51.307 --> 00:14:53.141
And she actually wanted to go?

00:14:53.142 --> 00:14:55.185
Seriously, it drives me crazy.

00:14:56.520 --> 00:14:57.521
No.

00:14:58.981 --> 00:15:00.274
It's good Mom doesn't know.

00:15:03.027 --> 00:15:04.945
If I'm honest,

00:15:05.446 --> 00:15:07.488
I think Mom should know too.

00:15:07.489 --> 00:15:10.492
How long has Dad been womanizing in the name of art?

00:15:14.288 --> 00:15:16.122
Should we just drop the bomb today?

00:15:16.123 --> 00:15:19.293
- To hell with his birthday. - No, you can't!

00:15:24.506 --> 00:15:27.927
Someone as sensitive as Mom wouldn't be able to handle it.

00:15:29.845 --> 00:15:31.305
Don't you remember?

00:15:31.805 --> 00:15:35.309
Years ago, when Mom was depressed, and she took some pills

00:15:35.893 --> 00:15:37.561
To kill herself.

00:15:39.939 --> 00:15:42.231
Mom must think I don't know, but I remember it all.

00:15:42.232 --> 00:15:43.859
But if she finds out about this...

00:15:46.612 --> 00:15:48.655
No. I'm going to protect Mom.

00:15:48.656 --> 00:15:51.116
Okay, I get it.

00:15:52.242 --> 00:15:54.828
That's why I'm keeping my mouth shut.

00:15:57.247 --> 00:16:00.541
But, fucking hell, this one is a real shocker.

00:16:00.542 --> 00:16:02.418
She used to work in our home!

00:16:02.419 --> 00:16:04.129
He's a real piece of shit.

00:16:05.297 --> 00:16:07.424
And to top it all off, that accident...

00:16:10.636 --> 00:16:11.637
But

00:16:13.138 --> 00:16:14.181
Min-hui...

00:16:16.809 --> 00:16:18.394
Didn't die from an accident.

00:16:20.396 --> 00:16:21.230
What?

00:16:22.189 --> 00:16:24.984
I couldn't bring myself to tell you over the phone.

00:16:25.651 --> 00:16:27.695
Then tell me now. What do you mean by that?

00:16:30.572 --> 00:16:31.865
Min-hui...

00:16:34.994 --> 00:16:36.578
Dad killed her.

00:16:38.706 --> 00:16:39.832
What did you say?

00:16:41.542 --> 00:16:42.793
Well, you see...

00:16:43.419 --> 00:16:44.461
Jeong-hu.

00:16:44.962 --> 00:16:45.796
Se-yun.

00:16:47.631 --> 00:16:48.465
Kim Jeong-hu.

00:16:49.800 --> 00:16:50.718
Kim Se-yun.

00:16:53.387 --> 00:16:55.972
Kang, where are the kids?

00:16:55.973 --> 00:16:57.599
Why aren't they answering?

00:16:58.517 --> 00:16:59.560
I don't know.

00:17:00.269 --> 00:17:01.353
I'm not really sure...

00:17:02.104 --> 00:17:05.190
Then could you come and take a look, Kang?

00:17:06.275 --> 00:17:07.109
Sorry?

00:17:24.043 --> 00:17:26.462
What do you think? Does it look okay?

00:17:28.255 --> 00:17:31.842
For some reason, I wanted to make it myself this year.

00:17:32.342 --> 00:17:33.427
What do you think?

00:17:34.428 --> 00:17:36.137
Should I add more decorations?

00:17:36.138 --> 00:17:39.600
No, it's good. Much prettier than the ones sold in stores.

00:17:40.225 --> 00:17:41.143
Really?

00:17:42.019 --> 00:17:42.978
You think so?

00:17:43.479 --> 00:17:44.605
Yes, really.

00:17:46.273 --> 00:17:47.483
I'll be going, then.

00:17:47.983 --> 00:17:48.984
What do you think

00:17:49.651 --> 00:17:52.154
I should write on top?

00:17:52.780 --> 00:17:55.157
Perhaps a unique birthday message?

00:18:00.079 --> 00:18:01.246
No way.

00:18:01.747 --> 00:18:03.749
No, you must have seen wrong.

00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:07.710
Sure, Dad's a bastard, but he wouldn't do that.

00:18:07.711 --> 00:18:09.420
No, I saw everything--

00:18:09.421 --> 00:18:11.048
I said it can't be true!

00:18:13.550 --> 00:18:14.551
<i>Unfortunately,</i>

00:18:15.052 --> 00:18:18.806
<i>the important part of the conversation was already over by the time I arrived.</i>

00:18:22.267 --> 00:18:23.894
What happened is

00:18:25.312 --> 00:18:27.480
You lost your mind from gaming too hard.

00:18:27.481 --> 00:18:28.815
A crazy hallucination.

00:18:28.816 --> 00:18:30.775
<i>- But I did learn...</i> - Don't say that!

00:18:30.776 --> 00:18:32.193
<i>...one crucial fact.</i>

00:18:32.194 --> 00:18:33.403
I told you.

00:18:33.904 --> 00:18:37.241
I secretly tailed them to the hospital after the accident.

00:19:00.597 --> 00:19:01.515
All right.

00:19:02.266 --> 00:19:04.518
Let's say, for argument's sake, that it's true.

00:19:05.227 --> 00:19:06.854
In that case,

00:19:07.521 --> 00:19:10.231
This wouldn't just be a scandalous affair.

00:19:10.232 --> 00:19:11.400
It would mean...

00:19:13.652 --> 00:19:15.988
The reputation that Dad's built up,

00:19:16.905 --> 00:19:18.823
And the world I've just stepped into...

00:19:18.824 --> 00:19:21.410
It would all go up in flames.

00:19:21.910 --> 00:19:22.744
You get that?

00:19:23.537 --> 00:19:25.497
- Jeong-hu. - You...

00:19:26.123 --> 00:19:27.791
Have you told anyone about this?

00:19:28.375 --> 00:19:29.209
Lee Kang.

00:19:29.877 --> 00:19:31.043
Did you tell him?

00:19:31.044 --> 00:19:33.797
Why would I tell anyone else? I only told you.

00:19:37.885 --> 00:19:40.971
Okay, that's fine. That's fine, then.

00:19:42.097 --> 00:19:43.181
Jeong-hu.

00:19:43.182 --> 00:19:44.473
Okay, yeah.

00:19:44.474 --> 00:19:47.102
Then you just need to keep your mouth shut. That's all.

00:19:47.603 --> 00:19:50.605
Thankfully, it seems like the police overlooked it, too,

00:19:50.606 --> 00:19:52.274
So everything's fine.

00:20:00.574 --> 00:20:01.992
Jeong-hu, you're really...

00:20:11.084 --> 00:20:12.753
You weak-ass piece of shit.

00:20:13.837 --> 00:20:15.422
If you don't do as I say,

00:20:16.465 --> 00:20:18.091
I will kill you.

00:20:19.092 --> 00:20:20.469
I'll make you pay.

00:20:32.981 --> 00:20:34.066
<i>Se-yun</i>

00:20:34.566 --> 00:20:36.777
<i>shut himself up in his room again.</i>

00:20:39.029 --> 00:20:42.074
Yun, what are you doing? Come out here.

00:20:43.408 --> 00:20:44.868
Jeong-hu's leaving.

00:20:48.038 --> 00:20:51.959
<i>He didn't even come out to see Jeong-hu off.</i>

00:20:56.546 --> 00:20:58.048
Are you okay, Mr. Heo?

00:21:04.221 --> 00:21:05.638
Well,

00:21:05.639 --> 00:21:08.100
I just heard so many shocking things.

00:21:10.227 --> 00:21:12.229
I don't even know where to start.

00:21:13.605 --> 00:21:14.690
I know, right?

00:21:15.232 --> 00:21:17.442
I was shocked at every turn too.

00:21:18.860 --> 00:21:21.196
I had no idea they had so many secrets.

00:21:22.656 --> 00:21:24.741
I see that house completely differently

00:21:25.242 --> 00:21:26.660
From my first visit now.

00:21:27.244 --> 00:21:28.245
In any case...

00:21:30.539 --> 00:21:32.040
We're back to square one.

00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:35.961
You didn't hear anything definitive.

00:21:36.461 --> 00:21:38.129
But one thing's for certain.

00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:42.049
Se-yun knows something. And he was at the hotel that day--

00:21:42.050 --> 00:21:44.052
That's right. That's it.

00:21:45.178 --> 00:21:47.931
He was definitely at the scene of the accident.

00:21:48.432 --> 00:21:50.851
And he tailed them to the hospital and saw something.

00:21:51.601 --> 00:21:52.519
Yes.

00:21:53.478 --> 00:21:55.439
That's the most surprising part.

00:21:58.191 --> 00:22:00.027
How did Se-yun know to go to the hotel,

00:22:01.236 --> 00:22:03.196
And what did he see at the hospital?

00:22:03.697 --> 00:22:04.781
But

00:22:05.615 --> 00:22:07.951
The kicker is that his own sister

00:22:08.535 --> 00:22:10.537
Muzzled him.

00:22:12.372 --> 00:22:16.877
So the key now is getting Se-yun to talk.

00:22:17.377 --> 00:22:20.297
Speaking of which, we need to take drastic measures.

00:22:21.590 --> 00:22:22.466
Drastic measures?

00:22:23.258 --> 00:22:26.094
I think we'll have to get Mrs. Ahn involved.

00:22:28.388 --> 00:22:29.473
- Eun-joo? - Yes.

00:22:31.892 --> 00:22:33.143
"Eun-joo"?

00:22:34.394 --> 00:22:36.187
Do you know her personally too?

00:22:36.188 --> 00:22:37.689
That's not important.

00:22:38.940 --> 00:22:40.775
Get her involved? How?

00:22:40.776 --> 00:22:46.073
Well, Mrs. Ahn is the only one left, since Jeong-hu is a lost cause.

00:22:46.573 --> 00:22:48.407
And there's no way he'll open up to me.

00:22:48.408 --> 00:22:51.994
So we give Mrs. Ahn a glimpse of the truth

00:22:51.995 --> 00:22:55.540
To make her question Se-yun herself.

00:22:56.041 --> 00:22:58.085
Right now, she knows nothing.

00:23:01.129 --> 00:23:03.172
Isn't that a good plan to find out more?

00:23:03.173 --> 00:23:04.383
No.

00:23:06.301 --> 00:23:07.134
Why not?

00:23:07.135 --> 00:23:09.096
Don't you remember what Se-yun said?

00:23:10.389 --> 00:23:11.932
He said his mom took pills

00:23:12.432 --> 00:23:14.309
And almost killed herself!

00:23:21.066 --> 00:23:24.110
You gotta pity the poor kid, being so worried about his mom, right?

00:23:24.111 --> 00:23:25.487
Still,

00:23:26.947 --> 00:23:30.075
It's the only shot we've got at finding out the truth.

00:23:35.372 --> 00:23:37.332
Now you're the one hesitating.

00:23:38.417 --> 00:23:39.501
Why is that?

00:23:40.377 --> 00:23:41.920
Is it because of Mrs. Ahn?

00:23:42.921 --> 00:23:44.297
Are you worried about her?

00:23:45.090 --> 00:23:47.426
- What's your relationship with her? - We're nothing!

00:23:47.926 --> 00:23:50.637
We're just acquaintances from my junior year in college!

00:23:51.805 --> 00:23:53.557
Satisfied? You punk.

00:24:01.356 --> 00:24:02.274
Anyway...

00:24:08.363 --> 00:24:11.741
We'll discuss this again at length later.

00:24:14.494 --> 00:24:15.745
Let's call it a day.

00:24:16.329 --> 00:24:18.540
I'm tired. Make sure to write everything up

00:24:19.124 --> 00:24:21.334
And submit your assignment as soon as possible.

00:24:38.768 --> 00:24:40.394
- Hey, what's up? <i>- Hello, Professor.</i>

00:24:40.395 --> 00:24:43.564
<i>Are you aware that there's an academic forum at 2:00 p.m. today?</i>

00:24:43.565 --> 00:24:45.483
<i>- The president asked.</i> - Right.

00:24:45.484 --> 00:24:47.444
<i>Since you haven't submitted your paper.</i>

00:24:50.447 --> 00:24:51.990
Okay, I'll send it over now.

00:24:54.075 --> 00:24:56.077
I said I got it. 2:00 p.m.

00:25:04.085 --> 00:25:09.090
I was just passing by and thought we could have lunch together.

00:25:10.342 --> 00:25:11.801
Okay, honey.

00:25:13.553 --> 00:25:16.348
Enjoy class. Okay.

00:25:16.932 --> 00:25:19.434
I'll see you at home. Bye.

00:26:49.608 --> 00:26:50.609
It's you.

00:26:51.901 --> 00:26:53.111
It's really you.

00:27:00.160 --> 00:27:01.411
Ahn Eun-joo.

00:27:02.746 --> 00:27:03.788
Eun-joo.

00:27:12.589 --> 00:27:14.799
TEACHING ASSISTANT KIM MI-SEO

00:29:24.179 --> 00:29:26.930
Honey, why did you come so early?

00:29:26.931 --> 00:29:28.682
Because I missed you, of course.

00:29:28.683 --> 00:29:29.976
You tease.

00:29:36.733 --> 00:29:38.275
Is it too cryptic?

00:29:38.276 --> 00:29:39.402
No, it's nice.

00:29:39.903 --> 00:29:41.196
There it is.

00:29:43.448 --> 00:29:44.783
- Right. - What do you think?

00:29:45.867 --> 00:29:46.951
Yeah, it's nice.

00:29:47.452 --> 00:29:49.788
Seeing those kids eat is making me hungry.

00:29:51.790 --> 00:29:53.500
Is it too dark?

00:29:54.125 --> 00:29:55.001
No.

00:29:56.085 --> 00:29:57.212
What do you want to eat?

00:29:58.004 --> 00:29:59.546
- Are you hungry? - Yeah.

00:29:59.547 --> 00:30:00.799
What should we eat?

00:30:03.051 --> 00:30:05.887
Should we have pasta? Or how about pizza?

00:30:06.387 --> 00:30:08.389
- Let's just order both. - Okay.

00:30:08.890 --> 00:30:10.099
There's one up there too.

00:31:16.875 --> 00:31:17.709
Eun-joo.

00:31:18.334 --> 00:31:19.377
Eun-joo.

00:31:24.465 --> 00:31:27.259
What do I do now? Now what do I do?

00:31:27.260 --> 00:31:28.761
What should I do?

00:31:35.894 --> 00:31:37.145
What do I do now?

00:31:45.403 --> 00:31:46.446
What do I do?

00:31:54.704 --> 00:31:56.497
What are you muttering to yourself?

00:31:57.665 --> 00:31:59.417
You haven't even changed your clothes.

00:32:04.631 --> 00:32:06.007
How about a glass of wine?

00:32:14.974 --> 00:32:18.185
The couple I met for their final session gave it to me today.

00:32:18.186 --> 00:32:20.104
They said they're doing much better.

00:32:23.107 --> 00:32:27.987
When they first came to see me, they were in a really bad place.

00:32:30.323 --> 00:32:31.199
But...

00:32:33.076 --> 00:32:35.912
After just a few sessions, things improved noticeably.

00:32:37.997 --> 00:32:41.376
It made me realize how important it is to talk.

00:32:46.881 --> 00:32:49.133
Why were you lying down like that earlier?

00:32:50.301 --> 00:32:51.386
Did something happen?

00:32:52.303 --> 00:32:53.763
You don't look so good.

00:32:55.765 --> 00:32:57.183
I'm just a little tired.

00:33:02.897 --> 00:33:06.859
Have you stopped those literature lessons? I liked how energetic they made you.

00:33:08.194 --> 00:33:11.280
I already told you. I'm not doing them anymore.

00:33:18.913 --> 00:33:21.457
So you won't sleep in my room anymore either?

00:33:24.377 --> 00:33:25.420
What is it...

00:33:27.296 --> 00:33:28.464
That you want to say?

00:33:37.056 --> 00:33:38.850
I want to apologize to you.

00:33:39.350 --> 00:33:41.019
I went too far that day.

00:33:45.732 --> 00:33:47.608
You know, the day we went to the movies.

00:33:48.860 --> 00:33:50.570
In the heat of the moment, I asked

00:33:51.654 --> 00:33:54.032
If you had an inferiority complex toward Kim Su-hun.

00:33:55.950 --> 00:33:58.161
What I said kept bothering me.

00:33:59.495 --> 00:34:00.872
I know

00:34:02.290 --> 00:34:04.876
Writers are sensitive about that kind of thing.

00:34:07.086 --> 00:34:09.672
I know better than anybody...

00:34:11.299 --> 00:34:13.550
How much you struggled when you couldn't write.

00:34:13.551 --> 00:34:15.011
That's enough.

00:34:17.180 --> 00:34:18.723
Why bring that up again?

00:34:20.433 --> 00:34:22.559
I'm just apologizing

00:34:22.560 --> 00:34:25.063
For crossing a line that day.

00:34:42.080 --> 00:34:43.706
What? Who is it?

00:34:47.460 --> 00:34:48.336
Honey.

00:34:49.587 --> 00:34:50.546
Honey?

00:35:05.103 --> 00:35:07.730
Hey, what's this? What picture is this?

00:35:08.439 --> 00:35:10.524
<i>A letter. I took a picture of a letter.</i>

00:35:10.525 --> 00:35:13.152
<i>A strange letter arrived at the house this afternoon.</i>

00:35:13.694 --> 00:35:14.529
A letter?

00:35:26.040 --> 00:35:27.208
What's this?

00:35:28.918 --> 00:35:30.503
There's no sender.

00:35:31.129 --> 00:35:32.420
Just your name.

00:35:32.421 --> 00:35:33.506
What?

00:35:34.966 --> 00:35:36.592
{\an8}KIM SU-HUN

00:35:38.761 --> 00:35:39.761
Welcome home.

00:35:39.762 --> 00:35:40.805
Hey.

00:35:41.764 --> 00:35:42.973
Is Yun home too?

00:35:42.974 --> 00:35:45.560
Yes, he's been gaming since he got home earlier.

00:35:49.522 --> 00:35:51.774
Then could you help put these away?

00:35:52.275 --> 00:35:53.984
I'm going to go and check in on Yun.

00:35:53.985 --> 00:35:55.778
Sure, go ahead. I'll put these away.

00:35:59.782 --> 00:36:00.616
Yun!

00:36:01.659 --> 00:36:03.161
Mom's home!

00:36:04.745 --> 00:36:07.582
We brought your favorite pizza from Mangwon-dong!

00:36:11.085 --> 00:36:12.044
What is it?

00:36:13.004 --> 00:36:13.921
Nothing.

00:36:14.547 --> 00:36:16.757
Just fan mail. Nothing important.

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:20.928
Fan mail?

00:36:22.180 --> 00:36:24.390
A handwritten letter, not an email?

00:36:25.516 --> 00:36:27.351
It happens from time to time.

00:36:27.894 --> 00:36:31.314
Older fans like this sort of sentimentality.

00:36:37.612 --> 00:36:38.905
Damn it.

00:36:47.121 --> 00:36:48.664
<i>Mr. Kim was acting strange.</i>

00:36:49.332 --> 00:36:50.958
<i>Even his hands were shaking.</i>

00:40:31.262 --> 00:40:32.971
I HAVE THE HOSPITAL CCTV FOOTAGE

00:40:32.972 --> 00:40:35.391
10 PM TONIGHT CENTRAL FOUNTAIN IN SEONGCHANG PARK

00:40:43.399 --> 00:40:44.733
Hospital CCTV footage?

00:40:46.694 --> 00:40:48.194
Does it really exist?

00:40:48.195 --> 00:40:50.989
<i>I don't know yet, but that's what the letter said.</i>

00:40:50.990 --> 00:40:52.324
Right.

00:40:53.367 --> 00:40:56.370
If the footage really exists, it would be the nail in the coffin.

00:40:57.788 --> 00:41:01.083
But who sent this letter? Was it Kim Se-yun?

00:41:01.584 --> 00:41:04.086
<i>- He's our best bet at the moment.</i> - Right.

00:41:04.920 --> 00:41:08.382
Kim Se-yun did mention the hospital to his sister.

00:41:09.425 --> 00:41:10.801
<i>Yeah, there's that,</i>

00:41:11.510 --> 00:41:13.179
<i>but something else happened.</i>

00:41:14.430 --> 00:41:15.305
Something else?

00:41:15.306 --> 00:41:17.850
<i>Yes, during dinner tonight.</i>

00:41:26.150 --> 00:41:28.818
This place's pizza really is the best way to lure Yun out.

00:41:28.819 --> 00:41:30.696
You were right, honey.

00:41:32.573 --> 00:41:33.407
What is it?

00:41:34.074 --> 00:41:35.743
What's on your mind, honey?

00:41:36.619 --> 00:41:37.453
Nothing.

00:41:38.120 --> 00:41:40.247
You're right. This place has the best pizza.

00:41:45.002 --> 00:41:49.340
How about we go see a late-night movie after this? It's been a while.

00:41:50.007 --> 00:41:51.216
A late-night movie?

00:41:51.217 --> 00:41:53.551
Or we could just go for a drive.

00:41:53.552 --> 00:41:55.303
Doesn't that sound wonderful?

00:41:55.304 --> 00:41:58.307
It'd be a waste to stay home on a night like this.

00:41:58.933 --> 00:42:01.851
No, I can't. I have plans, so I have to go out in a bit.

00:42:01.852 --> 00:42:04.771
Plans? What plans? All of a sudden?

00:42:04.772 --> 00:42:06.899
Yeah, suddenly. Mr. Choi asked to meet, so...

00:42:07.942 --> 00:42:10.069
You three should go to a movie or for a drive.

00:42:10.861 --> 00:42:14.031
Come on. It wouldn't be fun without you.

00:42:14.698 --> 00:42:15.991
I'll pass for today too.

00:42:16.492 --> 00:42:19.328
I'm meeting friends from my department at 10:00 p.m.

00:42:20.037 --> 00:42:22.121
You too? All of a sudden?

00:42:22.122 --> 00:42:24.124
It's not exactly sudden.

00:42:25.584 --> 00:42:27.253
I've been waiting for it for ages.

00:42:36.720 --> 00:42:38.472
<i>Se-yun's eyes looked different.</i>

00:42:39.765 --> 00:42:41.225
<i>As though he'd made up his mind.</i>

00:42:42.643 --> 00:42:46.230
I'm heading to the place mentioned in the letter now.

00:42:48.524 --> 00:42:49.525
Hey!

00:42:50.025 --> 00:42:53.654
You're heading there now? You're moving without my orders?

00:42:54.154 --> 00:42:55.573
<i>You said</i>

00:42:56.073 --> 00:42:59.368
<i>that when I'm conflicted, I should remind myself what all this is for.</i>

00:43:00.744 --> 00:43:01.661
What?

00:43:01.662 --> 00:43:03.956
<i>I'm going there to help my friend.</i>

00:43:07.585 --> 00:43:08.752
I see.

00:43:10.129 --> 00:43:12.298
<i>Se-yun's finally worked up the courage.</i>

00:43:12.798 --> 00:43:15.593
<i>If I witness that scene, I'll be able to find something out.</i>

00:43:21.557 --> 00:43:23.726
Okay, I understand. Go ahead.

00:43:24.268 --> 00:43:28.522
And call me as soon as it's over, okay?

00:43:29.857 --> 00:43:31.025
And one more thing.

00:43:31.984 --> 00:43:35.154
You must not get caught. You understand, don't you?

00:43:35.904 --> 00:43:36.864
Yes, I do.

00:43:38.073 --> 00:43:39.241
I'll call you.

00:44:10.522 --> 00:44:11.690
Honey.

00:44:15.319 --> 00:44:17.112
Why are you lying again?

00:44:17.655 --> 00:44:19.448
You said you stopped the lessons.

00:44:24.078 --> 00:44:26.330
And what was all that weird stuff you said?

00:44:27.456 --> 00:44:29.416
What did you mean about not getting caught?

00:44:30.542 --> 00:44:32.419
Eavesdropping again? How uncivilized.

00:44:34.588 --> 00:44:35.464
Uncivilized?

00:44:38.050 --> 00:44:39.593
If you're drunk, just go to bed.

00:44:40.636 --> 00:44:43.221
- Hey, Heo Mun-oh. - Stop it!

00:44:43.222 --> 00:44:45.557
I said stop it, okay?

00:44:46.350 --> 00:44:48.310
I told you to keep your nose out.

00:44:48.852 --> 00:44:49.895
Do you have any idea

00:44:50.854 --> 00:44:52.438
How serious the situation is?

00:44:52.439 --> 00:44:55.150
Serious? You mean, another thing I don't know about!

00:45:00.948 --> 00:45:02.866
Yeah, it's always been like this.

00:45:05.244 --> 00:45:06.954
You always had

00:45:08.580 --> 00:45:10.915
Something serious going on that I didn't know about.

00:45:10.916 --> 00:45:12.459
From the very start.

00:45:13.669 --> 00:45:17.756
Because you were writing or because you had writer's block.

00:45:21.885 --> 00:45:24.471
I was always here, and yet you never cared about me.

00:45:25.806 --> 00:45:26.849
Do you even know

00:45:27.850 --> 00:45:31.061
How shitty I feel whenever I do couples counseling?

00:45:31.562 --> 00:45:34.481
"Talk to each other constantly. Communication is key."

00:45:36.233 --> 00:45:37.943
That's what I tell them, yet I...

00:45:40.696 --> 00:45:41.613
We...

00:45:44.491 --> 00:45:46.994
You're the one who doesn't know a thing.

00:45:48.620 --> 00:45:51.247
How much I let slide.

00:45:51.248 --> 00:45:56.003
How long I've put up with you,

00:45:57.463 --> 00:45:58.881
Waited for you,

00:46:00.382 --> 00:46:01.967
And endured you.

00:46:04.303 --> 00:46:05.554
Do you have any idea?

00:46:09.641 --> 00:46:11.310
Quit your whining.

00:48:03.630 --> 00:48:04.714
<i>A comb? Nice.</i>

00:48:04.715 --> 00:48:06.424
<i>So you're not empty-handed.</i>

00:48:06.425 --> 00:48:08.427
<i>- A comb. - No one has their phone</i>...

00:48:20.022 --> 00:48:21.148
LEE KANG

00:48:30.198 --> 00:48:31.825
<i>The person you are calling</i>...

00:49:33.345 --> 00:49:34.262
What is it?

00:49:37.766 --> 00:49:39.226
Don't tell me that punk...

00:49:40.560 --> 00:49:41.770
At this hour?

00:49:54.366 --> 00:49:56.785
Mr. Heo, I know everything. Everything!

00:49:57.452 --> 00:49:59.496
- I know all of Mr. Kim's secrets-- - Quiet!

00:49:59.997 --> 00:50:00.831
Quickly, get in.

00:50:01.873 --> 00:50:03.374
I know everything. Really.

00:50:03.375 --> 00:50:05.085
Just get inside.

00:50:06.086 --> 00:50:07.045
Hurry.

00:50:16.388 --> 00:50:18.265
Have you totally lost it?

00:50:18.765 --> 00:50:20.058
How come you...

00:50:20.559 --> 00:50:22.184
Why did you come here at this time?

00:50:22.185 --> 00:50:25.896
Do you know what's even more shocking? Know what's even more riveting?

00:50:25.897 --> 00:50:27.523
You've seriously lost it.

00:50:27.524 --> 00:50:28.775
Mr. Heo, that young man

00:50:29.401 --> 00:50:30.986
Wasn't Se-yun.

00:50:31.611 --> 00:50:33.363
It wasn't Se-yun!

00:50:44.541 --> 00:50:46.626
Se-yun! It's me, Lee Kang!

00:50:47.127 --> 00:50:48.545
Hey, stop!

00:51:10.150 --> 00:51:12.486
What? That young man...

00:51:14.279 --> 00:51:15.739
Wasn't Kim Se-yun?

00:51:17.074 --> 00:51:18.408
No, it was Mrs. Ahn.

00:51:20.160 --> 00:51:21.578
Se-yun's mom.

00:51:22.329 --> 00:51:23.163
Ahn Eun-joo.

00:51:29.211 --> 00:51:30.295
Ahn Eun-joo?

00:51:53.944 --> 00:51:55.070
It was Eun-joo?

00:51:59.157 --> 00:52:00.659
It was dear Eun-joo?

00:52:04.121 --> 00:52:05.663
NOTES FROM THE LAST ROW

00:52:05.664 --> 00:52:07.082
<i>It was Eun-joo?</i>

00:54:33.228 --> 00:54:38.233
Subtitle translation by: Jimin Choi

